scripts.lightmap: bash -c "node vLm.map.js ; mv vLM_reportsmapViewTemplate-v-core9.com.html public/lightmap.html ; rm vLM_reportsmapViewTemplate-v-core9.com ; "
scripts.install: bash -c "node system/INSTALL/ ; npm install -g node-sass ; mkdir vLM_reports ; "
scripts.start_hosting: start bash -c " npm run start " && start bash -c "cd ~/.cloudflared/ ; cloudflared tunnel run ; "
scripts.dev: start bash -c "nodemon v9.host.js" && start bash -c "nodemon --exec 'npm run build_webapp'"
scripts.build_webapp: bash -c " rm -r -f public/ ; cp -r application/static/ public ;  node-sass application/style/SCSS/app.scss public/style/CSS/app.css ; npx webpack --config webpack.config.js ; "
